Package: deq
Title: A package to conveniently run DESeq2, edgeR, and QNB for the detection of differential methylation in MeRIP/m6A-seq data.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("A", "McIntyre", email = "abm237@cornell.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predicts differential methylation by implementing generalized linear models in DESeq2 or edgeR, or by running QNB. 
